  "comment": "The Event Lighting PAR12H is a durable and versatile LED Pro Parcan. With 12 x 12W RGBWA+UV LEDs, it delivers stunning colour combinations to suit any space. Enjoy customisable beam angles with options for 30˚, 40˚, 25˚ and 15˚, providing the perfect spread for any application. Experience 3,150 lux output at 2.0 meters, ensuring vibrant illumination in any setting. Boasting a robust lifespan of 50,000 hours, this fixture is built to last.\n\nWith 5 x 16-bit Dimming Curves and adjustable strobe settings ranging from 1 to 30Hz, you have full control over your lighting effects. Its flexible operational modes include DMX, auto run, sound active, and more, all easily navigated through the intuitive 4-button LCD control panel. Plus, with a sturdy die-cast aluminium housing and fanless cooling design, durability and reliability are guaranteed.\n\nThe PAR12H comes with True1 in/out, 5 pin DMX in/out and includes an omega bracket for quick and easy installation.",
